linear_equiv_det_conj_ae:
/-- The determinant of `conj_ae`, as a linear equiv. -/
@[simp]
theorem linear_equiv_det_conj_ae : conj_ae.to_linear_equiv.det = -1 := by
  rw [← Units.eq_iff, linear_equiv.coe_det, ← linear_equiv.to_linear_map_eq_coe,
    alg_equiv.to_linear_equiv_to_linear_map, det_conj_ae, Units.coe_neg_one]
#align linear_equiv_det_conj_ae linear_equiv_det_conj_ae
